Hakari: {
	PensamientoHakari: Hakari's thoughts

	Mision1: {
		Titulo: An Indirect Kiss
		Descripcion: Bring Hakari half a peach soda.
		Dialogo0: I'm craving a peach soda so much. Although, I could never finish a whole can all by myself...
		Dialogo1: In case you happened to find one... Do you... think that you could split it with me?
		Dialogo2: It's the perfect scheme! I'm so smooth! I'm totally about to land my first indirect kiss!
		Completacion0: Here, this feels about right.
		Completacion1: Thank you so much!
		Completacion2: Wait! Isn't this an... indirect kiss?
		Completacion3: His lips... have been right there...
		Completacion4: ...
		Completacion5: Huh? Hanazono?
		Completacion6: Listen to me... I... I love you! Please, {0}, please go out with me!
		Completacion7: Huh?! Really?!
		Completacion8: I'm sorry, I know this is so sudden.
		Completacion9: But I feel like I've already fallen head over heels for you.
		Completacion10: I don't think I'm the only one who loves you, so I wanted to say something while I can.
		Completacion11: I would rather embarrass myself than regret not trying.
	}

